316
00:19:32,468 --> 00:19:34,344
Bem-vindo.

317
00:19:35,345 --> 00:19:36,972
911.

318
00:19:41,685 --> 00:19:44,313
Pai, estás pálido.
Estás bem?

319
00:19:45,814 --> 00:19:49,068
Bestial.

320
